<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>RideShare program: survey confirmation.</h4>
    <p>
      Dear <%= "#{@faculty_survey.first_name} #{@faculty_survey.last_name}" %>,
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for submitting the survey.
      The program <%= link_to "#{Program.find(@faculty_survey.program_id).display_name_with_title}", program_url(Program.find(@faculty_survey.program_id)) %>
      was created based on your answers. You can edit the program data and add sites to the program at the above link.
      You can see and edit the survey here: <%= link_to "#{@faculty_survey.title}", faculty_survey_config_questions_url(@faculty_survey), class: "link_to" %>
    </p>
    <p>
      You can email <%= @unit_email %> or call the office at: <%= @contact_phone %> if you have any questions.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
